		<title>At least six dead in Brazil after powerful storm lashes Rio de Janeiro</title>

		<description>Rio de Janeiro, Brazil's second-largest city, awoke to scenes of chaos on Thursday after thrashing wind and rain whipped through neighborhoods, felling trees, flooding streets and sweeping away buses in a storm that killed at least six people.&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
